        <div class="block">
          <h2>My Design Philosophy</h2>
          <p>
            I believe learning isn’t just information — it’s an experience.
            Students engage more deeply when the interface feels intuitive and the content feels alive.
          </p>

          <p>So I focus on:</p>

          <ul>
            <li>Clear navigation and simple user flows</li>
            <li>Strong visual rhythm and colour</li>
            <li>Motion and micro-interactions</li>
            <li>Audio elements that support comprehension</li>
            <li>Minimal cognitive load</li>
            <li>Real-world relevance</li>
            <li>Accessibility across devices</li>
